description: Park Lawn Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides deathcare products and services in Canada and the United States. The company primarily offers cemetery lots, crypts, niches, monuments, caskets, urns, and other merchandise, as well as funeral, after life celebration, cemetery, and cremation services. It owns and operates 135 cemeteries and 138 funeral homes, as well as crematoriums. The company was founded in 1892 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
